<L>__{exterior derelict street day}
<A>__{joey's mazda 323 drives down the street. the daylight street is still creepy but in a different way; no bums, no trash can fires, nothing. it has the feel of a ghost town, as if nothing has breathed here for years.}
<B>__{angle in car}
<A>__{joey, at the wheel, has a disbelieving look on her face. terri, smoking, flicks ash through her wound down window.}
